verbose_text: ACR50 (the same instrument as ACR20, with improvement levels defined as 50% instead of 20%) response rates increased over time, with 20.1% of patients in the YLB113 arm and 23.2% in the RP arm achieving ACR50 responses at week 4, and 56.5 and 67.5% in the YLB113 and RP arms, respectively, achieving ACR50 responses at week 24.
